1
00:01:37,850 --> 00:01:41,020
[The Epoch of Miyu]

2
00:01:41,060 --> 00:01:44,000
[Episode 12]

3
00:01:50,000 --> 00:01:51,000
Hello, Mr. Ji.

4
00:01:51,620 --> 00:01:52,070
Hello.

5
00:01:52,070 --> 00:01:52,870
Hello, Mr. Ji.

6
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:56,640
Yin Xiang, let Ms. Xu come here.

7
00:01:56,640 --> 00:01:58,000
Okay, I'll go get her.

8
00:02:01,360 --> 00:02:02,160
Jia.

9
00:02:04,180 --> 00:02:05,140
Luo Qingping.

10
00:02:06,380 --> 00:02:07,300
Ke Wenxue.

11
00:02:20,870 --> 00:02:22,650
It's your working time now.

12
00:02:22,680 --> 00:02:24,510
Do the room attendants of Purong Hotel

13
00:02:24,510 --> 00:02:25,960
like to chat while working?

14
00:02:25,960 --> 00:02:27,120
I just wanted to provide guests

15
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,870
- with more attentive service.
- Then, do you know

16
00:02:28,870 --> 00:02:30,910
what the first principle of service is?

17
00:02:30,910 --> 00:02:32,310
It is not to disturb your guests.

18
00:02:32,310 --> 00:02:34,190
Could you go to any room

19
00:02:34,500 --> 00:02:35,760
on the executive floor

20
00:02:35,800 --> 00:02:37,750
and get me a bottle of shampoo?

21
00:02:37,800 --> 00:02:39,280
I know what you've discovered.

22
00:02:39,280 --> 00:02:41,340
But it is not the time to report it yet.

23
00:02:41,510 --> 00:02:42,390
I'm right here.

24
00:02:42,829 --> 00:02:43,810
Always?

25
00:02:43,980 --> 00:02:45,110
I'll always be here.

26
00:02:45,680 --> 00:02:46,560
Miyu.

27
00:02:47,870 --> 00:02:48,630
Miyu.

28
00:02:53,710 --> 00:02:55,190
What's more,
I noticed your hair accessories.

29
00:02:55,190 --> 00:02:56,520
They should be uniform.

30
00:02:56,590 --> 00:02:57,430
Understood?

31
00:02:59,380 --> 00:03:00,220
Ms. Xu.

32
00:03:00,370 --> 00:03:02,160
Mr. Ji.

33
00:03:02,600 --> 00:03:04,000
How is the check-in situation today?

34
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,190
Two check-ins

35
00:03:05,190 --> 00:03:06,310
and three check-outs.

36
00:03:06,310 --> 00:03:08,760
How did you handle the linens
in these rooms?

37
00:03:08,760 --> 00:03:10,670
We used freshly laundered linens
from the new factory

38
00:03:10,670 --> 00:03:12,390
and informed the guests.

39
00:03:12,410 --> 00:03:13,130
Good.

40
00:03:14,170 --> 00:03:16,050
No matter how many guests we have,

41
00:03:16,200 --> 00:03:18,040
our service must not slack off.

42
00:03:18,370 --> 00:03:19,810
Now, go back to your posts

43
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:21,420
and do your jobs well.

44
00:03:21,650 --> 00:03:22,370
Dismissed.

45
00:03:22,600 --> 00:03:23,440
Okay.

46
00:03:27,350 --> 00:03:29,200
You are the backbone
of the executive floor.

47
00:03:29,200 --> 00:03:30,510
Before the guests have left,

48
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:32,040
don't fall apart yourself.

49
00:03:42,070 --> 00:03:43,100
Room service.

50
00:03:45,450 --> 00:03:47,550
Hello, I am the forewoman
of the executive floor.

51
00:03:47,550 --> 00:03:49,440
May I help you?

52
00:03:49,910 --> 00:03:51,410
Close the door and come in.

53
00:03:52,210 --> 00:03:54,010
Whatever it is, just say it here.

54
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:58,900
You are Xu Miyu,

55
00:03:59,020 --> 00:04:00,820
the one trending online, right?

56
00:04:00,830 --> 00:04:03,630
I wonder who you're taking the blame for.

57
00:04:07,030 --> 00:04:07,270
[Xu Kai, Journalist]

58
00:04:07,100 --> 00:04:08,030
Don't be afraid.

59
00:04:08,240 --> 00:04:09,300
[Xu Kai, Journalist]

60
00:04:08,280 --> 00:04:09,280
I am a journalist.

61
00:04:10,080 --> 00:04:11,800
I know the corrupt upper management

62
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,830
will definitely use you,
lower-level staff, as scapegoats.

63
00:04:13,830 --> 00:04:14,590
Speak up.

64
00:04:14,630 --> 00:04:16,630
We in the media can speak out for you.

65
00:04:17,320 --> 00:04:19,589
Sorry, you misunderstood.

66
00:04:22,870 --> 00:04:24,040
You don't admit it

67
00:04:24,360 --> 00:04:26,150
because you're afraid of
getting into trouble, right?

68
00:04:26,150 --> 00:04:28,030
But you should know that
once this is exposed,

69
00:04:28,030 --> 00:04:29,470
no one can stay out of it.

70
00:04:29,490 --> 00:04:30,920
Just standing here, you are a story.

71
00:04:30,920 --> 00:04:31,600
Do you know that?

72
00:04:31,600 --> 00:04:32,630
I have no story.

73
00:04:33,630 --> 00:04:35,310
Please don't make one up.

74
00:04:37,870 --> 00:04:38,390
Do you know

75
00:04:38,390 --> 00:04:39,800
your silence means

76
00:04:39,800 --> 00:04:41,310
you are covering and indulging

77
00:04:41,310 --> 00:04:42,390
for illegal discipline?

78
00:04:42,390 --> 00:04:44,560
Because of people like you,
who refuse to report what you know,

79
00:04:44,560 --> 00:04:45,720
upholding justice

80
00:04:45,720 --> 00:04:47,190
becomes even harder.

81
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:48,900
Are you trying to frighten me?

82
00:04:52,750 --> 00:04:55,810
You must be Mr. Ji,
the new general manager here, right?

83
00:04:56,510 --> 00:04:58,970
Perfect. Let's sync up
on some information.

84
00:05:02,880 --> 00:05:04,680
Which media outlet are you from?

85
00:05:06,800 --> 00:05:07,670
Me?

86
00:05:07,900 --> 00:05:09,070
I am a freelancer.

87
00:05:09,070 --> 00:05:10,480
If all media were like you,

88
00:05:10,480 --> 00:05:12,120
the courts would be flooded
with subpoenas.

89
00:05:12,120 --> 00:05:14,360
You've already constituted a provocation.

90
00:05:14,360 --> 00:05:16,690
I can call the police
on behalf of the hotel

91
00:05:17,350 --> 00:05:19,750
and have your social media account banned.

92
00:05:29,410 --> 00:05:31,240
Ms. Xu. Ms. Xu.

93
00:05:31,270 --> 00:05:32,800
Mr. Feng wants you in his office.

94
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:33,630
Copy that.

95
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:35,820
Mr. Feng is looking for me.

96
00:05:35,950 --> 00:05:37,510
I'm afraid someone has already
made up a story about

97
00:05:37,510 --> 00:05:38,500
what happened to you

98
00:05:38,500 --> 00:05:40,060
and told Feng Kaixin.

99
00:05:41,159 --> 00:05:42,159
Go.

100
00:05:42,550 --> 00:05:44,159
You can only prove yourself
by going there.

101
00:05:44,159 --> 00:05:45,010
Okay.

102
00:05:53,650 --> 00:05:59,060
[Purong Hotel]

103
00:05:53,790 --> 00:05:55,920
I heard a reporter
interviewed you just now.

104
00:05:55,920 --> 00:05:56,920
What did you say to him?

105
00:05:56,920 --> 00:05:57,870
I didn't say anything.

106
00:05:57,870 --> 00:05:59,120
Don't pretend with me.

107
00:05:59,120 --> 00:06:00,750
So many people in the HSKP Department
saw it.

108
00:06:00,750 --> 00:06:01,950
How could I wrong you?

109
00:06:03,630 --> 00:06:04,870
Because of the detergent incident,

110
00:06:04,870 --> 00:06:06,510
I've already been very controversial.

111
00:06:06,510 --> 00:06:08,110
I know the power of the media.

112
00:06:08,150 --> 00:06:09,070
In this situation,

113
00:06:09,070 --> 00:06:10,120
if I talk nonsense,

114
00:06:10,120 --> 00:06:11,920
wouldn't I be asking for trouble?

115
00:06:11,920 --> 00:06:13,120
You talk a good game.

116
00:06:13,510 --> 00:06:14,190
But who knows what bad intentions

117
00:06:14,190 --> 00:06:15,360
you have in mind?

118
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,070
Follow me.

119
00:06:17,130 --> 00:06:18,250
We're going to see Mr. Wei.

120
00:06:18,250 --> 00:06:19,290
Why?

121
00:06:19,580 --> 00:06:20,610
You know the reason.

122
00:06:20,610 --> 00:06:21,820
It's because of what you did.

123
00:06:21,820 --> 00:06:22,630
Go.

124
00:06:23,020 --> 00:06:26,000
[Director's Office]

125
00:06:23,240 --> 00:06:25,040
Let's see what you say to Mr. Wei.

126
00:06:25,560 --> 00:06:27,220
- Stop pretending.
- Mr. Feng.

127
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:30,120
Mr. Ji.

128
00:06:31,480 --> 00:06:33,480
Mr. Ji, what brings you here?

129
00:06:34,560 --> 00:06:35,560
Ms. Xu is here too.

130
00:06:35,470 --> 00:06:38,510
[Director's Office]

131
00:06:36,130 --> 00:06:38,870
Yes, I was just about to report to you.

132
00:06:39,250 --> 00:06:39,750
She

133
00:06:39,950 --> 00:06:42,440
communicated privately with reporters
living on the executive floor.

134
00:06:42,440 --> 00:06:43,960
It is very unfavorable for us

135
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,390
to carry out crisis public relations.

136
00:06:45,390 --> 00:06:47,159
When Ms. Xu was being pestered,

137
00:06:47,180 --> 00:06:48,180
I saw everything.

138
00:06:49,780 --> 00:06:51,360
She didn't say a single word
to that journalist

139
00:06:51,360 --> 00:06:52,430
that would harm

140
00:06:52,430 --> 00:06:55,030
the reputation and interests of
Purong Hotel.

141
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:57,550
Ms. Xu was
deceived by the actual perpetrator,

142
00:06:57,550 --> 00:06:59,790
just like us.

143
00:07:00,310 --> 00:07:02,350
She's just a scapegoat.

144
00:07:04,200 --> 00:07:05,890
What do you say, Mr. Feng?

145
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:08,750
What a big mistake!

146
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,570
You have been wronged.

147
00:07:10,570 --> 00:07:11,690
I care so much

148
00:07:11,720 --> 00:07:12,990
about Purong Hotel

149
00:07:13,010 --> 00:07:15,300
that I was too stressed out from working.

150
00:07:15,400 --> 00:07:16,460
Please forgive me.

151
00:07:17,870 --> 00:07:18,680
Mr. Ji,

152
00:07:19,120 --> 00:07:20,240
do you have

153
00:07:20,240 --> 00:07:21,560
anything else to tell me?

154
00:07:21,560 --> 00:07:23,360
Or are you here just for Ms. Xu?

155
00:07:23,800 --> 00:07:26,070
I came here to remind you of
the meeting later.

156
00:07:26,070 --> 00:07:27,800
I hope you will be there on time.

157
00:07:28,960 --> 00:07:30,830
Don't dare to bother you.

158
00:07:30,870 --> 00:07:32,000
I was just about to go.

159
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:32,870
Shall we go?

160
00:07:33,180 --> 00:07:35,530
[Director's Office]

161
00:07:34,180 --> 00:07:34,750
Ms. Xu,

162
00:07:34,980 --> 00:07:35,840
go do your work.

163
00:07:44,860 --> 00:07:46,470
After you, Mr. Feng.

164
00:07:46,860 --> 00:07:48,010
After you.

165
00:07:54,680 --> 00:07:55,190
Excuse me.

166
00:07:55,190 --> 00:07:56,510
Hurry up! Make way.

167
00:08:04,330 --> 00:08:05,050
Mr. Feng.

168
00:08:08,770 --> 00:08:09,580
Take a look.

169
00:08:19,950 --> 00:08:21,210
[Total Bacteria: exceeding the limit]
[E. Coli: exceeding the limit]

170
00:08:25,570 --> 00:08:25,990
Mr. Wei.

171
00:08:25,660 --> 00:08:26,160
[Purong Hotel]

172
00:08:26,010 --> 00:08:27,340
- Mr. Wei.
- Mr. Wei.

173
00:08:26,180 --> 00:08:26,670
[Pujiang River Flows with Eternal Glory,
as Purong Hotel Accompanies You]

174
00:08:27,360 --> 00:08:27,950
Mr. Wei.

175
00:08:31,460 --> 00:08:33,990
[Purong Hotel]

176
00:08:37,000 --> 00:08:37,840
Sit.

177
00:08:37,780 --> 00:08:39,059
[Purong Hotel]

178
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:48,380
Mr. Wei, shall we start?

179
00:08:48,810 --> 00:08:49,690
Yes.

180
00:08:49,730 --> 00:08:50,660
No need to ask me.

181
00:08:51,280 --> 00:08:53,000
Some of you may not know yet.

182
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:53,960
Let me introduce.

183
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:56,250
This gentleman sitting in my seat is

184
00:08:56,270 --> 00:08:57,270
Ji Feng.

185
00:08:56,330 --> 00:08:57,990
[Purong Hotel]

186
00:08:57,550 --> 00:08:58,550
He is

187
00:08:58,020 --> 00:08:59,370
[Pujiang River Flows with Eternal Glory,
as Purong Hotel Accompanies You]

188
00:08:58,550 --> 00:09:00,630
the new general manager of Purong Hotel.

189
00:09:00,630 --> 00:09:02,430
Let's applaud to welcome Mr. Ji.

190
00:09:10,240 --> 00:09:12,930
[Purong Hotel]

191
00:09:12,350 --> 00:09:13,550
Thank you, everyone.

192
00:09:13,890 --> 00:09:15,510
It's my first time meeting you all

193
00:09:15,510 --> 00:09:17,750
and we run into such an emergency.

194
00:09:18,270 --> 00:09:19,930
It is indeed a bit unexpected.

195
00:09:20,550 --> 00:09:21,860
But the incident has already happened.

196
00:09:21,860 --> 00:09:23,130
We just have to face it.

197
00:09:24,360 --> 00:09:25,240
Mr. Feng,

198
00:09:26,120 --> 00:09:28,920
how does the HSKP Department
plan to handle it now?

199
00:09:30,200 --> 00:09:31,520
Here's the situation, Mr. Ji.

200
00:09:31,520 --> 00:09:32,610
As for the outsourced laundry factory,

201
00:09:32,610 --> 00:09:35,150
we terminated the contract
with it immediately.

202
00:09:35,150 --> 00:09:37,510
Now we have switched
to a new laundry factory,

203
00:09:37,510 --> 00:09:39,360
called Weimin Laundry Factory.

204
00:09:39,790 --> 00:09:40,960
Is it your way of

205
00:09:40,960 --> 00:09:42,160
solving the problem?

206
00:09:44,660 --> 00:09:45,800
The hotel linens

207
00:09:46,320 --> 00:09:47,960
have had excessive bleach for years.

208
00:09:47,960 --> 00:09:49,750
Is it simply a washing problem?

209
00:09:51,500 --> 00:09:53,110
Excessive bleach

210
00:09:53,170 --> 00:09:54,500
is the laundry's fault…

211
00:09:54,510 --> 00:09:56,360
How does the hotel supervise

212
00:09:56,360 --> 00:09:57,560
the laundry process?

213
00:09:57,710 --> 00:09:58,980
How often are the linens cleaned?

214
00:09:58,980 --> 00:10:00,250
What are the cleaning standards?

215
00:10:00,250 --> 00:10:02,220
Are there regular spot checks
by testing agencies?

216
00:10:02,220 --> 00:10:03,120
Mr. Feng, can you

217
00:10:03,120 --> 00:10:04,180
explain this to us?

218
00:10:05,540 --> 00:10:07,320
Well, I'm sorry.

219
00:10:07,320 --> 00:10:09,580
I have to go back and check the materials.

220
00:10:09,870 --> 00:10:12,210
This is not about checking materials.

221
00:10:12,230 --> 00:10:15,360
It's about the poor supervision of
the HSKP Department.

222
00:10:15,830 --> 00:10:16,960
From top to bottom,

223
00:10:17,670 --> 00:10:19,740
you turn a blind eye to inferior products.

224
00:10:19,740 --> 00:10:20,930
When problems occur,

225
00:10:20,930 --> 00:10:23,400
you let the bottom-level attendants
take the blame.

226
00:10:23,400 --> 00:10:25,030
Is this what the HSKP Department of

227
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:26,630
a five-star hotel should do?

228
00:10:27,310 --> 00:10:28,330
What we need to solve

229
00:10:28,330 --> 00:10:30,450
is not just the problem of the laundry.

230
00:10:30,450 --> 00:10:32,440
The whole linen supply chain of
the HSKP Department

231
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,680
should be changed.

232
00:10:35,800 --> 00:10:37,840
I don't think that's necessary.

233
00:10:37,870 --> 00:10:40,190
Excessive bleach

234
00:10:40,240 --> 00:10:42,240
is only a laundry compliance issue.

235
00:10:42,240 --> 00:10:43,810
There's nothing wrong with the linens.

236
00:10:43,810 --> 00:10:45,240
The fact that there's no problem
with the linens

237
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,370
doesn't mean the linens are flawless.

238
00:10:48,290 --> 00:10:49,440
Our bedding

239
00:10:49,730 --> 00:10:52,750
does not meet the standards
of a luxury hotel in itself.

240
00:10:52,750 --> 00:10:53,750
The guests on the executive floor

241
00:10:53,750 --> 00:10:55,320
are like‌ burnt children dread the fire.

242
00:10:55,320 --> 00:10:57,470
You don't want to get caught again, right?

243
00:10:57,470 --> 00:10:58,240
No.

244
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,860
I mean,

245
00:11:01,240 --> 00:11:03,100
changing the bedding supplier is

246
00:11:03,100 --> 00:11:05,050
a big deal.

247
00:11:05,480 --> 00:11:07,170
From product selection to trial,

248
00:11:07,170 --> 00:11:09,260
it will take at least two to three weeks.

249
00:11:09,260 --> 00:11:10,400
Not only does it waste money and manpower,

250
00:11:10,400 --> 00:11:12,560
but it can't solve an urgent problem.

251
00:11:12,600 --> 00:11:14,310
So you want to walk around it
when a big deal comes,

252
00:11:14,310 --> 00:11:15,070
right?

253
00:11:15,290 --> 00:11:16,560
Then, our concepts are really

254
00:11:16,560 --> 00:11:17,400
different.

255
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:19,720
Mr. Feng believes in muddling along,

256
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:22,580
while I prefer resolving the issue
once and for all.

257
00:11:24,830 --> 00:11:25,910
Everyone here is

258
00:11:25,910 --> 00:11:28,240
a management elite
in the hotel industry.

259
00:11:28,250 --> 00:11:29,670
Please use your resources

260
00:11:29,670 --> 00:11:31,790
to find a new bedding supplier.

261
00:11:32,050 --> 00:11:33,760
The quantity, price, and standard

262
00:11:33,760 --> 00:11:35,960
have been sent to your corporate email.

263
00:11:36,120 --> 00:11:38,750
Managers of each department
should collect all the proposals

264
00:11:38,750 --> 00:11:41,880
and submit them to my office
by the end of business today.

265
00:11:42,180 --> 00:11:43,310
Meeting adjourned.

266
00:11:56,050 --> 00:11:57,740
Mr. Wei asks you to take the initiative

267
00:11:57,740 --> 00:11:58,830
and make amends.

268
00:12:24,410 --> 00:12:25,320
You guys go first.

269
00:12:25,320 --> 00:12:26,380
Thank you, Mr. Ji.

270
00:12:44,510 --> 00:12:46,310
About the linen supplier issue,

271
00:12:46,370 --> 00:12:49,320
don't expect too much
from the subordinates.

272
00:12:49,630 --> 00:12:51,870
They are just here for a free ride.

273
00:12:51,900 --> 00:12:54,140
You need to understand your situation.

274
00:12:54,460 --> 00:12:55,360
You are anxious,

275
00:12:55,360 --> 00:12:56,480
but they are not in a hurry at all.

276
00:12:56,480 --> 00:12:57,270
I know.

277
00:12:57,870 --> 00:13:00,340
So I can take this opportunity to
see who is working

278
00:13:00,340 --> 00:13:01,310
and who is slacking off.

279
00:13:01,310 --> 00:13:03,710
Ji Feng, do you have that much time?

280
00:13:03,920 --> 00:13:06,480
Feng Kaixin was right at the meeting.

281
00:13:06,510 --> 00:13:07,970
If there's a major change,

282
00:13:08,160 --> 00:13:10,240
the transition period

283
00:13:10,260 --> 00:13:11,570
will be very painful.

284
00:13:11,670 --> 00:13:12,400
Don't worry.

285
00:13:13,030 --> 00:13:14,510
I've already contacted a laundry.

286
00:13:14,510 --> 00:13:15,810
We'll work with them
for three months first.

287
00:13:15,810 --> 00:13:17,030
We can change if it doesn't work out.

288
00:13:17,030 --> 00:13:19,250
I've also found backup suppliers.

289
00:13:19,270 --> 00:13:20,100
So fast?

290
00:13:21,030 --> 00:13:22,980
I cooperated with them
when I was at Siwei.

291
00:13:22,980 --> 00:13:24,040
We are old friends.

292
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:27,560
They will ship the goods
at this time tomorrow.

293
00:13:30,130 --> 00:13:30,890
Wait.

294
00:13:32,060 --> 00:13:34,030
Where did you get the money from?

295
00:13:34,600 --> 00:13:36,920
I haven't heard anything
in the finance department.

296
00:13:36,920 --> 00:13:39,190
That's the general manager's
emergency fund

297
00:13:39,190 --> 00:13:40,400
especially approved by the board.

298
00:13:40,400 --> 00:13:41,800
No one knows about it yet.

299
00:13:43,310 --> 00:13:44,820
Pretend to advance along one path

300
00:13:44,820 --> 00:13:46,700
while secretly attacking another.

301
00:13:46,700 --> 00:13:47,720
To break the monopoly

302
00:13:47,720 --> 00:13:48,890
and test

303
00:13:48,920 --> 00:13:50,650
where there will be a response.

304
00:13:51,100 --> 00:13:51,890
Awesome.

305
00:13:52,350 --> 00:13:53,280
I'm leaving now.

306
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:03,160
Okay, this cart is ready too.

307
00:14:03,160 --> 00:14:04,110
Go ahead.

308
00:14:06,990 --> 00:14:08,400
In just a few days,

309
00:14:09,030 --> 00:14:12,090
things have completely changed.

310
00:14:12,770 --> 00:14:14,910
Yesterday, we were still repeatedly
changing these linens,

311
00:14:14,910 --> 00:14:17,170
and today they all have to be cleared out.

312
00:14:17,960 --> 00:14:18,960
It's so deserted.

313
00:14:19,890 --> 00:14:21,690
Out with the old, in with the new.

314
00:14:21,710 --> 00:14:23,310
What's so good about the new?

315
00:14:23,440 --> 00:14:24,630
Let me tell you, if the new ones are good,

316
00:14:24,630 --> 00:14:25,840
they're harder to serve.

317
00:14:25,840 --> 00:14:26,550
Ms. Xu.

318
00:14:26,580 --> 00:14:28,820
Have the linens on the executive floor
been packed yet?

319
00:14:28,820 --> 00:14:29,360
Done.

320
00:14:29,360 --> 00:14:31,160
The last cart is coming right up.

321
00:14:38,550 --> 00:14:40,530
Do you think Miyu knew about it?

322
00:14:41,030 --> 00:14:41,960
Knew about what?

323
00:14:42,350 --> 00:14:45,430
About Mr. Ji becoming the general manager.

324
00:14:45,460 --> 00:14:47,440
Think about it. If she knew,

325
00:14:47,750 --> 00:14:50,010
could she be an undercover sent by Mr. Ji?

326
00:14:50,050 --> 00:14:52,410
Madam Cailu got into trouble

327
00:14:52,440 --> 00:14:53,460
and Drunkard Feng got bad luck,

328
00:14:53,460 --> 00:14:54,870
while she became the forewoman.

329
00:14:54,870 --> 00:14:56,530
Doesn't it all make sense now?

330
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,550
Could she be the big boss
behind the scenes?

331
00:14:59,550 --> 00:15:00,550
Big boss?

332
00:15:02,270 --> 00:15:04,320
If she were the big boss,

333
00:15:04,870 --> 00:15:07,150
would Drunkard Feng be able to
bully her like that?

334
00:15:07,150 --> 00:15:09,080
Drunkard Feng and Mr. Wei

335
00:15:09,080 --> 00:15:10,750
are in the same boat.

336
00:15:11,030 --> 00:15:13,030
But Mr. Ji pushed out Mr. Wei.

337
00:15:13,390 --> 00:15:14,590
Doesn't it all add up?

338
00:15:14,790 --> 00:15:17,150
If you put it that way,

339
00:15:18,010 --> 00:15:20,520
she's the general manager's favorite.

340
00:15:21,410 --> 00:15:22,530
If that's the case,

341
00:15:22,560 --> 00:15:24,450
couldn't she even
get a little overtime pay?

342
00:15:24,450 --> 00:15:26,250
Do you believe she didn't get it?

343
00:15:26,390 --> 00:15:28,750
Maybe she pocketed it all.

344
00:15:30,700 --> 00:15:33,030
Miyu isn't that kind of person.

345
00:15:37,030 --> 00:15:38,980
[HSKP Department Management Work Group]

346
00:15:40,000 --> 00:15:42,750
Notice to all managers, supervisors,
forewomen, and foremen.

347
00:15:42,750 --> 00:15:45,350
We are now collecting information
on linen suppliers.

348
00:15:45,350 --> 00:15:47,460
Please fill out the proposal template

349
00:15:47,460 --> 00:15:50,620
and submit it to the HSKP Department
corporate email by the end of the day.

350
00:15:50,620 --> 00:15:52,630
Have you finished tidying up
the linens on your floor?

351
00:15:52,630 --> 00:15:53,750
Just finished.

352
00:15:54,300 --> 00:15:55,630
Did you see the message in the group?

353
00:15:55,630 --> 00:15:58,000
I did, but it has nothing to do with us.

354
00:15:58,020 --> 00:15:59,500
How could we

355
00:15:59,530 --> 00:16:02,040
have any channels for linen suppliers?

356
00:16:02,150 --> 00:16:04,440
Feng's notices are getting
more and more ridiculous.

357
00:16:04,440 --> 00:16:06,220
He dares to make any kind of request.

358
00:16:06,220 --> 00:16:07,410
Just ignore him. I guess

359
00:16:07,410 --> 00:16:09,480
he's rushing to flatter the new boss.

360
00:16:09,500 --> 00:16:11,220
So, he just said it,

361
00:16:11,250 --> 00:16:13,070
and we just forget it.

362
00:16:20,320 --> 00:16:22,630
[Purong Hotel]

363
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:29,630
Ms. Xu.

364
00:16:31,180 --> 00:16:32,440
I thought you weren't here.

365
00:16:32,440 --> 00:16:34,240
I saw you hung the cleaning sign.

366
00:16:35,390 --> 00:16:37,270
I intended to go out.

367
00:16:37,440 --> 00:16:38,920
Just tidy up a bit.

368
00:16:38,950 --> 00:16:39,710
Okay.

369
00:16:40,110 --> 00:16:40,960
By the way.

370
00:16:41,680 --> 00:16:43,240
Thank you

371
00:16:43,570 --> 00:16:45,810
for helping me out with that reporter,

372
00:16:47,000 --> 00:16:49,000
and for the media exchange meeting.

373
00:16:49,120 --> 00:16:50,250
Thank you very much.

374
00:16:53,750 --> 00:16:56,150
I just hope you can
pull yourself together.

375
00:16:57,150 --> 00:16:59,030
We are in the same boat now.

376
00:16:59,390 --> 00:17:01,790
If you don't want Purong Hotel to

377
00:17:01,790 --> 00:17:02,920
decline gradually,

378
00:17:03,030 --> 00:17:05,000
we have to pull together.

379
00:17:05,260 --> 00:17:06,020
Understand?

380
00:17:10,010 --> 00:17:10,940
Get back to work.

381
00:17:11,460 --> 00:17:12,060
Okay.

382
00:17:17,109 --> 00:17:17,960
Hi, Martri.

383
00:17:21,170 --> 00:17:21,890
What?

384
00:17:22,640 --> 00:17:24,530
The goods are stuck at customs?

385
00:17:25,740 --> 00:17:26,770
Come on.

386
00:17:27,369 --> 00:17:28,329
Martri,

387
00:17:28,720 --> 00:17:29,920
I'm serious.

388
00:17:32,800 --> 00:17:34,600
How long will it be held on?

389
00:17:36,050 --> 00:17:39,250
Oh, please try something out
with the customs officials.

390
00:17:39,280 --> 00:17:40,570
I need a final date

391
00:17:40,590 --> 00:17:43,590
and announce it at the press conference

392
00:17:43,620 --> 00:17:45,220
tomorrow.

393
00:17:45,920 --> 00:17:46,890
Okay.

394
00:17:54,450 --> 00:17:55,810
Is Mr. Liu there?

395
00:17:58,130 --> 00:18:00,520
I'll go find him right away.

396
00:17:58,910 --> 00:18:00,280
[Purong Hotel]

397
00:18:00,550 --> 00:18:02,000
Please let him know.

398
00:18:14,510 --> 00:18:15,240
Hello.

399
00:18:15,400 --> 00:18:16,480
Asilan,

400
00:18:16,480 --> 00:18:17,630
can you hear me?

401
00:18:17,960 --> 00:18:21,240
I can't hear you clearly.
Please wait a moment.

402
00:18:23,720 --> 00:18:24,400
Hello.

403
00:18:25,070 --> 00:18:26,790
The machines inside are too loud.

404
00:18:26,790 --> 00:18:27,960
Ms. Xu.

405
00:18:27,960 --> 00:18:30,200
Are the guesthouse beddings
working out well?

406
00:18:30,200 --> 00:18:31,750
Do you need to restock?

407
00:18:31,750 --> 00:18:33,640
They're great.
I'm not restocking this time.

408
00:18:33,640 --> 00:18:34,970
I'm placing a new order.

409
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:36,030
How many?

410
00:18:36,480 --> 00:18:37,720
2,000 sets of

411
00:18:37,720 --> 00:18:39,830
13-piece bedding set,
including slippers.

412
00:18:39,830 --> 00:18:41,000
Can you supply that?

413
00:18:41,000 --> 00:18:42,160
That's a lot.

414
00:18:42,310 --> 00:18:44,700
Your guesthouse business must be booming.

415
00:18:44,700 --> 00:18:45,880
It's not for the guesthouse this time.

416
00:18:45,880 --> 00:18:47,640
It's for a five-star hotel.

417
00:18:47,640 --> 00:18:50,030
If you can keep the high-quality,

418
00:18:50,050 --> 00:18:51,840
we'll order even more.

419
00:18:51,860 --> 00:18:52,750
Aslan,

420
00:18:52,780 --> 00:18:53,750
can you hurry up

421
00:18:53,750 --> 00:18:55,160
to send me a sample?

422
00:18:55,160 --> 00:18:56,550
How soon can it arrive?

423
00:18:56,550 --> 00:18:58,880
Tomorrow. It'll arrive tomorrow.

424
00:18:58,880 --> 00:19:00,280
I'll expedite it for you.

425
00:19:00,450 --> 00:19:01,440
Don't forget to send me

426
00:19:01,440 --> 00:19:02,920
your product qualification certificates.

427
00:19:02,920 --> 00:19:04,440
Okay, I'll send them right away.

428
00:19:04,440 --> 00:19:05,070
Goodbye.

429
00:19:05,070 --> 00:19:06,480
Okay, that's it. Bye.

430
00:19:07,410 --> 00:19:07,850
[Aslan]

431
00:19:07,870 --> 00:19:08,490
[Yunhai Cotton Mill, Brand Introduction]

432
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:11,740
[Test Report]

433
00:19:20,890 --> 00:19:24,540
[Director's Office]

434
00:19:25,590 --> 00:19:27,050
Ms. Xu, what's the matter?

435
00:19:27,350 --> 00:19:30,030
I'm here to submit the proposal
for the linen supplier.

436
00:19:30,030 --> 00:19:31,170
Just leave it to me.

437
00:19:31,890 --> 00:19:34,040
Can I hand it to Mr. Feng myself?

438
00:19:34,070 --> 00:19:35,200
There are some details

439
00:19:35,200 --> 00:19:37,200
that I want to explain to him in person.

440
00:19:37,200 --> 00:19:38,440
Mr. Feng is with a client right now.

441
00:19:38,440 --> 00:19:39,570
He's not available.

442
00:19:39,640 --> 00:19:43,100
Okay, please pass it on to him for me.

443
00:19:42,720 --> 00:19:44,840
[Director's Office]

444
00:19:43,240 --> 00:19:45,240
Thank you for your hard work, Ms. Xu.

445
00:19:47,270 --> 00:19:50,980
[Director's Office]

446
00:19:55,920 --> 00:19:59,230
[Director's Office]

447
00:20:02,740 --> 00:20:03,370
Mr. Li.

448
00:20:03,770 --> 00:20:04,770
This price cut is

449
00:20:04,790 --> 00:20:06,230
just for show.

450
00:20:06,590 --> 00:20:08,750
We'll make the proposal look good to

451
00:20:08,830 --> 00:20:10,360
secure the contract first.

452
00:20:10,440 --> 00:20:11,410
Next time,

453
00:20:11,440 --> 00:20:13,440
we'll raise the price back.

454
00:20:13,460 --> 00:20:14,310
Okay?

455
00:20:17,500 --> 00:20:18,020
Yes.

456
00:20:21,090 --> 00:20:22,970
[Supplier Proposal: Yunhai Cotton Bedding]

457
00:20:22,990 --> 00:20:24,580
[Proposer: Xu Miyu]

458
00:20:30,630 --> 00:20:31,530
Yes. Yes.

459
00:20:34,090 --> 00:20:34,370
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

460
00:20:34,500 --> 00:20:37,260
[Supplier Introduction]

461
00:20:37,400 --> 00:20:37,670
[Cooperation Plan]

462
00:20:43,550 --> 00:20:45,590
For our long-lasting cooperation,

463
00:20:46,820 --> 00:20:47,740
my treat tonight, okay?

464
00:20:47,740 --> 00:20:49,070
We can talk while we eat.

465
00:20:49,620 --> 00:20:50,420
Okay.

466
00:20:55,030 --> 00:20:56,890
Book a private room
at Yuhuating Restaurant for me tonight.

467
00:20:56,890 --> 00:20:58,640
Mr. Feng, as for that proposal...

468
00:20:58,640 --> 00:20:59,990
Keep it here.

469
00:21:00,600 --> 00:21:01,750
Don't let Ji see it.

470
00:21:01,790 --> 00:21:03,450
Then, this deal won't be done.

471
00:21:04,480 --> 00:21:06,210
Dare she try to compete with me?

472
00:21:09,060 --> 00:21:13,810
[Supplier Proposal: Yunhai Cotton Bedding]

473
00:21:31,370 --> 00:21:34,910
[Purong Hotel]

474
00:21:36,240 --> 00:21:39,220
[Purong Hotel]

475
00:21:47,670 --> 00:21:48,670
[Supplier Proposal:
Xianglong Bedding Introduction]

476
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:49,810
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

477
00:21:49,890 --> 00:21:50,530
[Supplier Proposal:
Xianglong Bedding Introduction]

478
00:21:50,740 --> 00:21:51,250
[Xianglong Bedding Cotton Mill
Bedding Supply Plan]

479
00:22:00,270 --> 00:22:01,510
Just one proposal?

480
00:22:01,830 --> 00:22:03,160
From yesterday to today,

481
00:22:03,160 --> 00:22:04,790
only Mr. Feng from the HSKP Department

482
00:22:04,790 --> 00:22:06,510
submitted a proposal.

483
00:22:07,510 --> 00:22:09,280
Okay. Thanks for your hard work.

484
00:22:09,280 --> 00:22:10,090
No problem.

485
00:22:18,230 --> 00:22:22,040
[General Manager's Office]

486
00:22:26,640 --> 00:22:27,470
Come in.

487
00:22:35,750 --> 00:22:36,440
Mr. Wei.

488
00:22:36,690 --> 00:22:39,040
Mr. Feng from the HSKP Department
has submitted the proposal.

489
00:22:39,040 --> 00:22:39,970
Here is a copy.

490
00:22:41,480 --> 00:22:42,660
[Supplier Proposal:
Xianglong Bedding Introduction]

491
00:22:42,730 --> 00:22:44,440
[Purong Hotel Supplier Registration Form]

492
00:22:48,470 --> 00:22:49,670
Okay, go ahead.

493
00:23:02,460 --> 00:23:03,350
Mr. Feng.

494
00:23:03,620 --> 00:23:04,430
Mr. Qian.

495
00:23:04,540 --> 00:23:09,710
[Do not block the door.
Violators will receive a written warning]

496
00:23:14,750 --> 00:23:16,880
Bro, we have a deal.

497
00:23:16,900 --> 00:23:19,380
I'll be the only one
submitting the proposal.

498
00:23:19,380 --> 00:23:21,140
I will let Ji have no choice.

499
00:23:21,880 --> 00:23:23,840
Let's make sure we don't fight
amongst ourselves.

500
00:23:23,840 --> 00:23:26,640
Don't worry. I've already
made the arrangements.

501
00:23:27,680 --> 00:23:29,340
I can always count on you, bro.

502
00:23:31,440 --> 00:23:32,680
But

503
00:23:33,110 --> 00:23:35,590
why hasn't Ji come to me?

504
00:23:36,030 --> 00:23:37,010
Does he have

505
00:23:37,320 --> 00:23:39,270
other proposals?

506
00:23:40,400 --> 00:23:42,200
He's new to the job.

507
00:23:42,440 --> 00:23:44,480
He needs to save face.

508
00:23:44,720 --> 00:23:46,090
Stay calm.

509
00:23:46,960 --> 00:23:48,880
He's the one who needs you.

510
00:23:49,110 --> 00:23:50,680
You don't need him.

511
00:23:57,020 --> 00:23:57,840
I'm leaving.

512
00:24:08,030 --> 00:24:10,230
Any news from the customs negotiation?

513
00:24:11,410 --> 00:24:12,550
Why is it taking so long?

514
00:24:12,550 --> 00:24:13,950
We can't wait any longer.

515
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:16,410
I need an answer as soon as possible.

516
00:24:16,410 --> 00:24:18,310
[Purong Hotel]

517
00:24:17,170 --> 00:24:18,640
Is Mr. Tao back?

518
00:24:19,720 --> 00:24:21,110
At the court? Which court?

519
00:24:20,530 --> 00:24:23,520
[Purong Hotel]

520
00:24:22,550 --> 00:24:23,790
Please contact him for me.

521
00:24:23,790 --> 00:24:25,250
I'll head there right now.

522
00:24:26,140 --> 00:24:27,770
[To Xu Miyu] [From Aslan]

523
00:24:29,710 --> 00:24:30,430
Thank you.

524
00:24:38,440 --> 00:24:39,240
Secretary Wu.

525
00:24:39,680 --> 00:24:41,610
We're off work. Mr. Wei isn't here,

526
00:24:41,720 --> 00:24:43,070
and neither is Mr. Ji.

527
00:24:43,130 --> 00:24:44,400
I'm not looking for them.

528
00:24:44,400 --> 00:24:45,760
I just want to ask you a question.

529
00:24:45,760 --> 00:24:46,830
Did you receive

530
00:24:46,830 --> 00:24:48,200
the bedding supplier proposals

531
00:24:48,200 --> 00:24:49,930
for the HSKP Department today?

532
00:24:50,450 --> 00:24:51,540
Why do you ask?

533
00:24:51,570 --> 00:24:52,910
I delivered a proposal.

534
00:24:53,000 --> 00:24:55,310
It has color pictures of the cotton fields

535
00:24:55,310 --> 00:24:56,200
in the northwest.

536
00:24:56,200 --> 00:24:57,590
I have no idea.

537
00:24:57,590 --> 00:24:59,130
When the general manager arrives tomorrow,

538
00:24:59,130 --> 00:25:00,530
you can ask him yourself.

539
00:25:01,900 --> 00:25:04,100
Sorry to keep you from getting off work.

540
00:25:30,200 --> 00:25:31,270
Hello, Mr. Tao.

541
00:25:31,270 --> 00:25:33,160
Yes, I just arrived at the hotel.

542
00:25:33,640 --> 00:25:35,900
I'll send the contract to you right away.

543
00:25:39,900 --> 00:25:42,490
Add another hundred yuan for each set?

544
00:25:43,940 --> 00:25:44,790
But Mr. Tao,

545
00:25:45,070 --> 00:25:47,710
we just agreed on the price an hour ago.

546
00:25:51,920 --> 00:25:54,160
Okay, let me think about it.

547
00:26:18,670 --> 00:26:19,310
Mr. Ji.

548
00:26:19,480 --> 00:26:21,400
I saw you weren't here just now,

549
00:26:21,400 --> 00:26:23,130
so I changed the bedding first.

550
00:26:23,180 --> 00:26:24,440
I was waiting for you to come back.

551
00:26:24,440 --> 00:26:26,310
I didn't ask for new bedding.

552
00:26:26,770 --> 00:26:29,110
This is a sample from the factory.

553
00:26:29,110 --> 00:26:30,960
I wanted to show it to you

554
00:26:30,960 --> 00:26:31,900
before the new product launch.

555
00:26:31,900 --> 00:26:34,110
But your schedule is fully booked,

556
00:26:34,110 --> 00:26:35,550
so I could only...

557
00:26:42,210 --> 00:26:43,310
[Washing instructions]

558
00:26:42,630 --> 00:26:44,030
Where is this brand from?

559
00:26:44,110 --> 00:26:46,200
Yunhai is a cotton processing plant

560
00:26:46,200 --> 00:26:47,400
