836
00:38:49,040 --> 00:38:50,480
will not be tolerated.

837
00:38:50,900 --> 00:38:53,100
Anyone who slacks off at their post

838
00:38:53,130 --> 00:38:54,470
and just makes up the numbers

839
00:38:54,470 --> 00:38:56,320
will be punished accordingly.

840
00:38:56,870 --> 00:39:00,110
They will be demoted, receive pay cuts,
or even dismissed.

841
00:39:00,110 --> 00:39:02,110
Mr. Feng,

842
00:39:02,720 --> 00:39:04,920
do you have anything else to talk about?

843
00:39:05,050 --> 00:39:06,410
No, no.

844
00:39:07,320 --> 00:39:10,450
Good. We'll discuss the rest
at the directors' meeting.

845
00:39:11,180 --> 00:39:12,310
Meeting adjourned.

846
00:39:24,280 --> 00:39:25,920
[Transaction alert: Amount 10,000 yuan]

847
00:39:26,790 --> 00:39:28,190
I wish it were given to me.

848
00:39:39,860 --> 00:39:40,620
Okay.

849
00:39:42,850 --> 00:39:43,490
[Transaction in progress, please wait]

850
00:39:43,560 --> 00:39:45,250
[Preparing cash, please wait]

851
00:39:50,840 --> 00:39:53,510
We've all worked just as hard.

852
00:39:53,760 --> 00:39:54,840
Why did she just talk

853
00:39:54,840 --> 00:39:56,440
and get a 10,000-yuan bonus,

854
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:58,590
while we don't even get overtime pay?

855
00:39:58,590 --> 00:40:00,480
She is Mr. Ji's favorite.

856
00:40:00,480 --> 00:40:01,280
If there are any perks,

857
00:40:01,280 --> 00:40:02,880
she'll definitely get them.

858
00:40:03,040 --> 00:40:05,320
How can we compare to her?

859
00:40:05,800 --> 00:40:07,880
We all did the work.

860
00:40:07,920 --> 00:40:09,800
But when it came to bonuses,
she took it all.

861
00:40:09,800 --> 00:40:10,440
Why?

862
00:40:10,440 --> 00:40:11,060
Exactly.

863
00:40:11,090 --> 00:40:12,770
Without us bottom-level workers,

864
00:40:12,770 --> 00:40:14,500
how could she claim any credit?

865
00:40:14,610 --> 00:40:15,610
Listen.

866
00:40:16,070 --> 00:40:18,190
We shouldn't listen to her anymore.

867
00:40:18,190 --> 00:40:20,440
We won't get any benefits
no matter how well we do anyway.

868
00:40:20,440 --> 00:40:22,440
Aren't you afraid she'll make things
difficult for you?

869
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:24,150
If we all present a united front,

870
00:40:24,150 --> 00:40:26,080
she can't possibly wipe us all out.

871
00:40:29,400 --> 00:40:30,730
Why are you two so quiet?

872
00:40:31,550 --> 00:40:33,300
Don't drag me into your rebellion.

873
00:40:33,300 --> 00:40:33,990
Childish.

874
00:40:36,960 --> 00:40:38,030
Yin Xiang,

875
00:40:38,050 --> 00:40:40,140
aren't you going to suck up to her?

876
00:40:41,520 --> 00:40:43,030
Harmony brings wealth.

877
00:40:43,050 --> 00:40:44,690
Why make things so tense?

878
00:40:45,510 --> 00:40:46,400
Actually,

879
00:40:46,950 --> 00:40:47,960
Miyu isn't

880
00:40:47,960 --> 00:40:49,800
as difficult
to deal with as you think.

881
00:40:49,800 --> 00:40:51,520
She can be persuaded by reason
but not cowed by force.

882
00:40:51,520 --> 00:40:52,410
So,

883
00:40:52,430 --> 00:40:53,690
instead of going against her,

884
00:40:53,690 --> 00:40:55,070
it's better to just go along with her.

885
00:40:55,070 --> 00:40:57,570
Yes. She's quite nice,

886
00:40:57,600 --> 00:40:59,260
even a bit of a bleeding heart.

887
00:40:59,480 --> 00:41:01,200
We can just play the pity card with her.

888
00:41:01,200 --> 00:41:03,390
Just say, "Miyu, please,

889
00:41:03,440 --> 00:41:06,170
help me out, I can't do it."

890
00:41:06,230 --> 00:41:08,090
She'll immediately act like a cat

891
00:41:08,590 --> 00:41:09,990
which is sniffed catnip,

892
00:41:10,010 --> 00:41:11,300
getting all high.

893
00:41:11,410 --> 00:41:12,590
Then everything will

894
00:41:12,590 --> 00:41:14,320
just fall into place, won't it?

895
00:41:14,350 --> 00:41:15,960
We can take time off when we want,

896
00:41:15,960 --> 00:41:17,440
and slack off when we want.

897
00:41:17,460 --> 00:41:19,710
Anyway, she'll take care of
all the remaining work for you.

